肺炎日记|2月15日：极端雨雪冲击武汉，医疗增援远超汶川。
Pneumonia Diary & # 124; Feb. 15: Extreme rain and snow swept Wuhan, and medical assistance went far beyond Wenchuan.
2020-02-16 07:59:55来源： 财新网作者：黄蕙昭责任编辑：任波。
2020-02-16 07: 59: 55 Source: Caixin net author: Huiwei responsible editor: Ren Bo.
2020年02月16日 07:59。
16 February 2020 07: 59.
来源于。
From sources.
财新网。
Caixin Net.
可以听文章啦！。
Listen to the passage.
目前有近2.5万医务人员驰援武汉，医疗救援调动规模和速度大大超过汶川地震；而雷神山医院多处病区因极端雨雪出现漏水，接收病患的计划恐将延后。
Nearly 25,000 medical personnel rushed to Wuhan, the scale and speed of medical relief mobilization greatly exceeded Wenchuan earthquake, and many of the Lei Shenshan Hospital disease areas due to extreme rain and snow leakage, the plan to receive patients will be delayed.
2020年2月15日，武汉中午前后转雨夹雪，下午雨夹雪转中到大雪，气温陡降，到今晚20时接近0℃。
February 15, 2020, Wuhan around noon around the sleet, in the afternoon rain and snow into the snow, the temperature dropped steeply, by 20 o'clock tonight near 0 ℃.
图/财新记者 丁刚。
Photo / Finance new reporter Ding Gang.
相关报道解药|不止钟南山指导的团队，多款新冠快检技术冲刺中武汉仍有少量新冠病人未入院 隔离点治疗能力不足需重视极端雨雪天气致雷神山医院漏水  收治计划延后肺炎日记|2月14日：“清零”重压下，武汉社区的曲折战事肺炎日记|2月13日：那些死于肺炎的患者。
Not only has Zhong Nan Shan supervised the team, but Wuhan still has a small number of new crowns. There are still a small number of unhospitalized patients with inadequate treatment capacity in Wuhan.
【财新网】（记者 黄蕙昭 综合）2月14日晚至15日，正在抗击新冠疫情的武汉遭遇大风和雨雪，极端天气为防控战事蒙上一层阴霾：雷神山医院数处病区出现漏水，接收病患的计划恐将延后。
From Feb. 14 to Feb. 15, Wuhan, which is battling the new crown, was hit by high winds and sleet. Extreme weather clouded the fight against the disease. Several areas at Raytheon Mountain Hospital were leaking and plans to receive patients threatened to be delayed.
另一面，武汉保卫战攻坚克难步伐不停，据官方最新消息，目前有近2.5万医务人员驰援武汉，医疗救援调动规模和速度大大超过汶川地震。
Wuhan, on the other hand, is struggling to keep pace with the latest official news, nearly 25,000 medical personnel rushed to Wuhan, medical rescue mobilization scale and speed greatly than the Wenchuan earthquake.
。
.
2020年2月14日0时-24时，全国新型冠状病毒肺炎新增确诊病例2641例（其中湖北省临床诊断病例1138例）、新增死亡病例143例、新增疑似病例2277例、新增重症病例849例，新增确诊、死亡、疑似、重症病例较2月13日分别变化-48.1%、18.2%、-7.1%、-60.9%。
On February 14, 2020, between 0000 and 2400 hours, 2,641 new cases of coronavirus pneumonia (1,138 cases of clinical diagnosis in Hubei Province), 143 new cases of death, 2277 new suspected cases and 849 new cases of serious illness were recorded.
（见：【数据解析】新冠疫情分析简报（2月14日））。
(See: New Crown Epidemic Analysis Bulletin (14 February).)
尽管全国新增重症病例增速显著降低，对武汉而言，大量重症、危重症病人仍是首要难题。
Although the growth rate of new serious cases has decreased significantly in China, a large number of serious and critical patients are still the most difficult problems in Wuhan.
“现在武汉重症病例大概占所有确诊病例和住院病例的18%左右。
"Wuhan now accounts for about 18 percent of all confirmed cases and hospitalizations.
” 2月15日，国新办在湖北武汉举行新闻发布会，国家卫健委医政医管局副局长焦雅辉介绍，这些患者从发病到住院的时间比较长，很多在入院时就已经是重症和危重状态。
"On February 15, the State Administration of Health held a press conference in Wuhan, Hubei Province, where the deputy director of the National Health Administration, Jiao Yahui, said the patients had been in hospital for a relatively long time.
。
.
大量重症和危重症病人极大考验武汉医疗系统人力和物力，“外援”成扭转战局的核心力量之一。
A large number of seriously ill and critically ill patients greatly tested Wuhan medical system manpower and material resources, "foreign aid" into a reversal of the war one of the core forces.
截至2月14日，各地共派出217支医疗队，25633名医疗队员（不含军队医疗队和队员），其中在武汉市有181支医疗队，20374名医疗队员。
As at 14 February, 217 medical teams had been dispatched to various localities, with 25,633 medical personnel (excluding military medical teams and members), including 181 medical teams and 20,374 medical personnel in Wuhan city.
国家卫健委副主任、湖北省委常委王贺胜强调，本次医疗救援的调动规模和速度已大大超过了2008年汶川特大地震。
The deputy director of the National Health Committee, Hubei Provincial Standing Committee Wang He Sheng stressed that the scale and speed of medical rescue mobilization has greatly exceeded the Wenchuan earthquake in 2008.
（见：国家卫健委：武汉重症占比18% 很多入院已是重症）。
(See: National Fitness Committee: Wuhan accounts for 18% of the severe cases have been admitted to the hospital is severe).
抗疫关键口，天公不作美，一场猛烈雨雪为防抗计划带来冲击。
Anti-epidemic key mouth, weather is not beautiful, a heavy rain and snow for the anti-attack plan impact.
据财新记者了解，极端雨雪天气下，刚刚建成交付的雷神山医院多处病区出现漏水，15日接收病患的计划恐将延后，同时，部分已启用的病区迫于漏水只能临时转移受影响的病人。
According to the new reporter, extreme rain and snow weather, just completed delivery of Lei Shenshan Hospital in many areas of the leaking, 15-day plans for patients will be delayed, and some of the patients have been opened because of leakage can only temporarily transfer affected patients.
目前，施工单位正在抓紧维修整改。
At present, the construction unit is stepping up repair.
（见：极端雨雪天气致雷神山医院漏水 收治计划延后）。
(See: Delayed admission plan for Lei Shenshan Hospital due to extreme rain and snow).
财新记者同时了解到，“清零”要求下，武汉仍有少量新冠病人未入院。
The new reporter also learned that "clean zero" requirements, Wuhan is still a small number of new crown patients have not been hospitalized.
部分隔离点虽然配有医护人员，但基本没有对症治疗，只是每天统一测量体温，发一些抗病毒口服液和中药制剂，一些隔离点甚至缺水断电。
Although some of the isolation points have medical staff, but basically no symptomatic treatment, only a unified daily temperature measurement, some antiviral oral liquid and Chinese medicine, some isolation points even water and electricity.
“很多人在这种隔离点里面待着，其实是加重了病情。
"A lot of people who stay in this sort of isolation are actually making things worse.
”一位患者亲属说。
"said a relative.
（见：武汉仍有少量新冠病人未入院 隔离点治疗能力不足需重视）。
(See: Wuhan still has a small number of new crown patients unhospitalized isolation site treatment capacity needs to pay attention).
疫情前期大量病患无法及时收治入院，部分是因为新冠肺炎确诊流程长、检测结果存误差，如何推动诊断筛查前移、下移，成为近期科研热点。
A large number of patients could not be admitted to hospital in time, partly because of the long process of diagnosis of new crown pneumonia and the error of the test results.
2月14日，中国工程院院士钟南山指导下的广州医科大学呼吸疾病国家重点实验室宣布，联合多家机构研发出了新型冠状病毒IgM抗体快速检测试剂盒，希望将抗体检测等快检技术与现行的核酸检测形成互补，降低漏检风险。
On February 14, the State Key Laboratory of Respiratory Diseases of Guangzhou Medical University under the guidance of Zhong Nan Shan, a member of the Chinese Academy of Engineering, announced that a new coronavirus IgM antibody rapid detection kit had been developed by several organizations.
此外，麻省理工学院教授张锋团队的新技术也进入公众视野。
In addition, MIT professor Zhang Feng's team's new technology has also entered the public eye.
（见：解药|不止钟南山指导的团队，多款新冠快检技术冲刺中）。
(See: Not just the team at Zhong Nan Shan. Many of the new fast-track technology sprints.)
今日值得关注的另一则动态来自邻国：新型冠状病毒疫情向境外传播之际，日本的动向受到广泛瞩目。
Another development that deserves attention today is that of neighboring countries, where the new coronavirus epidemic is spreading overseas, and Japan's movement is widely noted.
截至2月15日，日本国内共检出337名确诊感染者，其中日本境内发现的感染者有52例，在“钻石公主”号上发现的感染者达285例，是中国之外疫情最显著的国家。
As of February 15, 337 confirmed cases had been detected in Japan, including 52 in Japan and 285 on board the Princess Diamond, making it the most affected country outside China.
。
.
从新冠疫情发生之始，顾虑到观光经济和东京奥运会等需求，日本政府的应对对策相对保守，仅一边倒地强调“边境防守”对策。
From the start of the new crown, anxious about the economy of tourism and the demand for the Tokyo Olympics, the Japanese government's response has been relatively conservative, with only a one-sided emphasis on "border defense."
日本专家纷纷呼吁，随着日本被迫进入应对新型冠状病毒的新阶段，应该以承认“国内流行为前提”，转变相关政策。
Japanese experts are calling for a shift in policy in recognition of a "domestic epidemic" as Japan is forced into a new phase in its response to the new coronavirus.
2月15日，日本厚生劳动相加藤胜信承认，从2月13日之后，日本国内出现多个“无法弄清明确感染途径”的病例，这使得日本政府对疫情的评估“已与此前的状况不同”。
Japan's health minister admitted on Feb. 15 that since February 13, there had been a number of cases of "unclear route of infection," making the government's assessment of the epidemic "different from what it was before."
（见：分析|日本防疫为何迷失 日政府承认疫情流行进入新阶段）。
(See: Analysis and # 124; Why the Lost Day Government acknowledges that the epidemic has entered a new phase).
